(175323, '934A4D8D-6A0F-4061-9647-96BBBE942374', 'Enjoy your kids tonight ', '460268762000000000', '460268763000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-02T21:26:02'),
(175407, 'E9170B35-DA7B-4ED8-A961-958F7A050D94', 'One last thought: your desire for building a new kind of partnership at this stage in life is really inspiring to me. And you are showing me every day that it''s not just a pie in the sky dream. You''re willing to do the work that goes along with making that dream a reality. It''s one of the things I like most about you. ', '460268876000000000', '460268880000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-02T21:27:56'),
(175284, '2C45B96A-09FD-45B9-830D-E48C3633C800', 'Thank you for keeping me company on my first day in my new place. I''m anxious to get it all dialed in and have it feel like my own. Sorry that this meant at times I wasn''t as present for you...and didn''t make that clear. You made me realize it is a bad habit creeping in. I''m used to Marla talking at me, and she really isn''t looking for engagement, just hearing her voice...and when I got busy, it didn''t take much focus or energy to kind of listen. It is all part of what I feel in many respects is a reinvention of my identity. You reminded me that some of the same tools from work, like appreciative inquiry, can help us.  when I let myself think too much about the future, I get a bit scared. I''m getting super sleepy.  ', '460300236000000000', '460300251000000000', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'David', '2015-08-03T06:10:36'),
