(175320, 'FBCEAABA-013D-48EF-B383-B41CA4FD167A', 'Thanks for this super honest reflection my dear. ', '460302383000000000', '460302384000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T06:46:23'),
(175465, '4800A012-CD4E-4F20-8849-EC34FC85C9B4', 'The good news (or bad news depending on how you see this) is that I have a very high bar for what kind of partnership I want to build. And have some really clear ideas about what that looked like. All of our exchanges yesterday were a perfect example of meeting that bar. ', '460302386000000000', '460302386000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T06:46:26'),
(175392, '44E53823-8624-4070-8E43-5D673877730F', 'But I want to be clear about what I mean by meeting the bar. I thought you weren''t a great listener during the day, and I didn''t love how you responded initially to my high holiday questions (and was hoping you''d see some of the reading in between the lines stuff). So this is where relationships tend to break down: one person raises this stuff and the other gets defensive or offended or doesn''t want to acknowledge the challenge altogether. You did none of those things. You listened, you reflected, you went deeper into thinking about what kinds of habits you may have gotten into from years of having one partner. All of which is totally understandable. You acknowledged, you listened, you showed me you cared in many ways on that call. And we even talked about ways we could have that conversation differently. ', '460302388000000000', '460302388000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T06:46:28'),
(175305, '01B1D9A3-AC54-4895-B48A-4CBA11CE00F6', 'I too am loving all the different facets of you and the way our dynamic is developing. You are so sweet, and patient, and articulate. I like that we have different life experiences but are not defined by them. And that you can see in me not just who I am but who I could be and visa versa.', '460302394000000000', '460302528000000000', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'David', '2015-08-03T06:46:34'),
(175431, 'AB6C172C-EE39-4A9D-A163-1EF4F28E0A0E', 'I found you to be so open to improving the way you engage, because what you want is what I want -- a higher bar for what partnership means. I care a lot less about the actual ''infractions'' and care a lot more about how the conversations happen after that. Do they have love and warmth in them. Are they affectionate. And do they lead to a new set of ideas for things we can test out in the future. You were amazing on that call last night and this text with your own reflections only solidifies that for me more. ', '460302472000000000', '460302472000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T06:47:52'),
(175417, 'C6DE7233-5126-427D-9E41-7A60FA00BAD9', 'There are many many people who are not up for this kind of partnership. It''s hard work. But the payout is a much more meaningful relationship. And for me, I cannot settle for anything less. ', '460302473000000000', '460302473000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T06:47:53'),
(175345, '045DAB1E-5F6A-40CE-A56D-FDDFD75F8766', 'For a bit of context. I had hoped and attempted furiously for the last year to try and have this type of engagement with Marla. She literally says ''you should just love me for who I am.''  I knew there was no future here because growth and learning and sharing had become a dead end. I''ve really been humbled over the last 2yrs and I''m hungry to become better...a better partner, dad, friend, brother, colleague. I already have a glimpse at how much more I can offer and how much richer life can/will be. Still early days. I feel so lucky to have found you. Who knows where things lead, but let''s appreciate now. You are bringing great joy.  I''m going to quote the great poet Bono, who recently sang, ''a heart that is broken, is a heart that''s left open.''  You treat my open heart gently and with kindness, sensitivity, empathy and compassion. I promise to do the same, and if I  stray, please call me on It. One of the things I love about you is that you would do the same not just for me, but for any person you met. It is deeply engrained in your being. You are a rare gem my dear. ', '460303543000000000', '460303587000000000', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'David', '2015-08-03T07:05:43'),
(175385, '32B08856-B4C0-4F80-BF6B-444126460BCE', 'And if you were here. You''d see (little) tears in my eyes. ', '460303701000000000', '460307056000000000', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'David', '2015-08-03T07:08:21'),
(175389, '5B1FCF61-328A-4168-B479-85A1CFA8B0B6', 'You will learn about me...maybe come to enjoy, that I find a soundtrack for many times of the day to fit the moment. Right now it is Lost in the Dream by The War on Drugs. (Under the Pressure).', '460303846000000000', '460307056000000000', 1, 'David', 'Nitzan', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'David', '2015-08-03T07:10:46'),
(175294, '50900198-71AC-4E99-8E20-632281BAE835', 'It''s funny. I was going to write something about the people who say ''love me for who I am.''  In some ways, Marla isn''t wrong. If you are with someone who you think you can''t accept for all of who they are right now, you probably shouldn''t be with them. ', '460308329000000000', '460309113000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T08:25:29'),
(175374, 'B976A27F-112A-42F0-AA43-EB7FB2189E12', 'What I like about us is that we both have a deep commitment to growth. And I see, at the heart of it, how good you are. ', '460308373000000000', '460309113000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T08:26:13'),
