(175322, '12FF8F04-56BE-4C1E-8059-8CFBF151E7A1', 'It’s been a really nice day. Laurel, the person I’m building out this ED training for said that if it weren’t for my work two weekends ago in Jacksonville, it would have been a total failure. And then Aline, from Rwanda, wrote this text message in response to some of our back and forth saying “At times I wonder what I did to deserve such a good friend...” ', '460323750000000000', '460323770000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T12:42:30'),
