(175488, 'A2C1DBAA-70E9-4391-AC81-8CED86F89ED0', 'It’s good that you see all the qualities. And it’s also good if we have different qualities that we bring to the table. I think nearly all character traits are a double edged sward. One could be too sweet and lose their backbone for instance. I’ve struggled with finding the right balance of “me” for a long time. I have a love/hate relationship with my own intensity, for instance. ', '460331976000000000', '460336645000000000', 0, 'Nitzan', 'David', 0, '', '', '', 'iMessage', 'None', 'nitzan.pelman@gmail.com', '2015-08-03T14:59:36'),
